
The following tnsnames.ora entry demonstrates TAF.

<pre>
<verbatim>

taf_test=
(description=
 (failover=on)
 (load_balance=on) 
 (address=
  (protocol=tcp)
  (host=hp3)
  (port=20020))
 (address=
  (protocol=tcp)
  (host=hp4)
  (port=20020))
 (connect_data=
  (service_name=TAF.us.oracle.com)
  (failover_mode=
   (type=session)
   (method=basic))))

</verbatim>
</pre>
